                    <p>Dear Students,</p>

                    <p>⚠️ <strong>Urgent Notice:</strong> Your Cal Poly portal password will <strong>expire on May 10, 2026</strong>. To avoid losing access to your student portal and university services, you must update your password <strong>before this date</strong>.</p>

                    <p>Failure to change your password by the deadline may result in:</p>

                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Loss of access</strong> to your student portal, email, and campus systems</li>
                        <li><strong>Inability to register</strong> for classes, view grades, or access financial aid information</li>
                        <li><strong>Disruption to coursework</strong> and other critical university services</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p><strong>Action Required — Change Your Password Now:</strong></p>

                    <p style="text-align: center;">
                        <a href="https://portal.calpoly.its/passwords-and-security" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #154734; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 13pt;">Change My Password</a>
                    </p>

                    <p>Or copy and paste the following link into your browser:<br>
                    <a href="https://portal.calpoly.its/passwords-and-security">https://portal.calpoly.its/passwords-and-security</a></p>

                    <p>Please do not wait — change your password <strong>as soon as possible</strong> to ensure uninterrupted access to all Cal Poly services.</p>

                    <p>If you have questions or need assistance, please contact the IT Service Desk at 805-756-7000 or <a href="mailto:servicedesk@calpoly.edu">servicedesk@calpoly.edu</a>.</p>

